Iran said it had achieved importantvictories against Iraq on the southern war fronts last night.    A brief Iranian news agency IRNA report said "Importantvictories achieved in southern fronts Monday night." It gave nofurther details.    Iran launched a major offensive, codenamed Karbala-5,towards the major southern Iraqi port of Basra in January, butthere have been no reports of heavy fighting in the area inrecent weeks. REUTER&#3;